{"tid":1549034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"乜嘢叫無需再叫人fact check？你班友係咪傻撚咗？","createTime":"2019-09-07T07:44:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T11:50:37.000Z","uid":3904,"like":123,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"064f4505b4a88368cc6440b8e236ab29780f824e","tid":1549034,"uid":3904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:44:16.000Z","msg":"今日個post叫人燒山，焦土本身就唔係咩問題，但佢第一句就叫人無需要再fc就極之大問題。<br />\n<br />\n我哋同班藍絲最大嘅地方，就係我哋所相信嘅資訊係源於事實，而唔係乜嘢流言都走去信一餐。新屋嶺單嘢，雖然係有機會真係死咗人，但只要未有實証，都唔可以當真係發生咗，<span style=\"color: red;\">因為死咗人係好大獲</span>，1%炒車嘅機會都唔可以有！ <br />\n<br />\n就好似假義載真強姦咁，我係相信有，但亦都唔敢同人講肯定發生過。然而，義載非禮女仔我就可以好肯定有，因為我而家就處理緊一單，個女仔一直精神好唔穩定，要照顧佢同時又要想辦法刮個仆街陷家剷出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋而家要贏，就一定要靠文宣，尤其係國際文宣，因為香港暫時仲未變成新疆最大嘅原因在於全世界都睇住。任何嘅勇武行為，都一定要出師有名，因為國際文宣實在經唔起炒大車，我唔知點同CNN解釋燒錯山！"},{"pid":"5e87a2066f17fd7591f4931accf43d6bd5ebecbf","tid":1549034,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:45:08.000Z","msg":"不斷製造炒車係因為真相已經流出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531194\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531194</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4a43cf65d480cbed4364a9524dfa921a06dc0bdf","tid":1549034,"uid":47672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:45:23.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"4100d3d4e8b41de73cb2a2e1ffb4f9dc61e9e918","tid":1549034,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:45:40.000Z","msg":"Fact Check 文化已經將呢場運動擊潰<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1548807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1548807</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504c943ba0bc1c709ac6c9319ae132835640884f","tid":1549034,"uid":169492,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:45:42.000Z","msg":"加個合理懷疑就夠。 <br />\n可以繼續文宣。"},{"pid":"c22df906c5909c263f30ea6702d3ca2462ed1997","tid":1549034,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:46:38.000Z","msg":"好多五毛 真心膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a01371095478d6b4f7d9dbe03c9fd8280ee02f6","tid":1549034,"uid":94771,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:47:35.000Z","msg":"合理惑疑可以有 但唔好講到100%咁<br />\nfc不嬲到開始到依家的精神 唔好不利自己就放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b103d6b5878ae67ba270619c27aad296881a4ba","tid":1549034,"uid":279513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:47:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"834eb91c88c06144c246c316b4715e1a471824ff","tid":1549034,"uid":269629,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:47:57.000Z","msg":"唔fact check，咪等同藍絲廢老一樣？<br />\n文宣做得成功，因為道理係我地依邊。唔係circulate假新聞假消息而黎。<br />\n貪一時之快講多兩次，就唔會再有人信抗爭者既說話，係之後都唔會再信。<br />\n冷靜，再出發。"},{"pid":"7eb4077d91de3b4b0ca80227b6b16775c851482e","tid":1549034,"uid":297835,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:48:37.000Z","msg":"其實講唔洗fc 個d五毛<br />\nBlock<br />\n上一頁<br />\n完"},{"pid":"4187b49fa15a156f896b34dcb553eb21fc2c7425","tid":1549034,"uid":3904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"504c943ba0bc1c709ac6c9319ae132835640884f","tid":1549034,"uid":169492,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:45:42.000Z","msg":"加個合理懷疑就夠。 <br />\n可以繼續文宣。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:51:50.000Z","msg":"合理懷疑還合理懷疑<br />\nFC還FC<br />\n<br />\n總唔可以合理懷疑就走去燒山掛？"},{"pid":"824efb211fe49ccce0ed5479da836207b9c079a4","tid":1549034,"uid":201862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:52:29.000Z","msg":"推比更多手足知"},{"pid":"e014eb0ce2c2e3cec6774a979622ced5d0934c7f","tid":1549034,"uid":131484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:53:14.000Z","msg":"冇錯，唔fc同藍絲冇分別，就係聽自已鐘意聽的野"},{"pid":"861720635a6c28995aff0b937a8a8321b6ebd109","tid":1549034,"uid":103230,"